                           <p>Some of the leaves have suffered from dampness and are damaged,
                              especially at the inner margin. The inner margin of fol.
                                 <locus>25</locus> and the bottom margin of fol. <locus>27</locus>
                              have been excised. There are lacunae after fols <locus>1, 5, 8, 9, 14,
                                 18, 19, 21, 23 and 24</locus>.</p>
                        </condition>
